{"tid":1577312,"cid":18,"subCid":6,"title":"睇中醫真係好神奇","createTime":"2019-09-17T15:36:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-14T08:07:54.000Z","uid":59014,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"feb85495b6a6ce23bdf8d96084ee48490bded0c0","tid":1577312,"uid":59014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T15:36:01.000Z","msg":"把下我脈, 睇睇手掌, 伸下條利<br />\n就執左幾劑藥比你, 又話你腎虛<br />\n<br />\n我忍唔住咁快見完醫生, 事關真係病到嘔彩<br />\n問佢屋企有食呢隻野, 問佢有無用<br />\n佢搖搖頭 無直接答 最後up左某D中醫既terms <br />\n然後又搖搖頭"},{"pid":"cb4a4774056e9b97f7bc121caa63f4a68b3c9e4f","tid":1577312,"uid":82993,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T15:36:15.000Z","msg":"呢筆債，佢哋一定要還。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1576589\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1576589</a>"},{"pid":"ddeaaa526edee0ffdc0ca7c5b6f701f957c1dd50","tid":1577312,"uid":35508,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T15:39:02.000Z","msg":"唔係好明第2段<br />\n但中醫真係好work<br />\n之前半個月黎一次m 維持左半年<br />\n又係話我腎虛<br />\n食左一個月中藥變番準"},{"pid":"e175a06548314de865e9ec4f3df90fd5c15974e2","tid":1577312,"uid":59014,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ddeaaa526edee0ffdc0ca7c5b6f701f957c1dd50","tid":1577312,"uid":35508,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T15:39:02.000Z","msg":"唔係好明第2段<br />\n但中醫真係好work<br />\n之前半個月黎一次m 維持左半年<br />\n又係話我腎虛<br />\n食左一個月中藥變番準"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T16:22:20.000Z","msg":"絲兄, 我又係腎虛"},{"pid":"010e9e576da0e0db7e14c450b902809eaf84ea9e","tid":1577312,"uid":125246,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T16:41:03.000Z","msg":"有中醫名嗎？"},{"pid":"09e697f39ffa979649a573b9d22e2bd7bd954318","tid":1577312,"uid":324309,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T15:47:17.000Z","msg":"我唔明，點解你咁懷疑中醫仲會去睇。"},{"pid":"13ce60f6f63a6d242d2b0de77af6f2967951f1f4","tid":1577312,"uid":46752,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T06:36:09.000Z","m