hkgmoji\" /><br />\n例如我前兩日病到仆街，<br />\n尺脈嘅脈象係明顯弱<br />\n今日好返少少就變中間強度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有興趣可以睇下個blog<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://dmke.pixnet.net/blog/post/220139621-%E4%B8%AD%E9%86%AB%E6%8A%8A%E8%84%88%E5%8E%9F%E7%90%86%EF%BC%8C%E6%94%B6%E8%97%8F%E5%A5%BD%EF%BC%81%E6%B2%92%E4%BA%8B%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E4%B9%9F%E8%83%BD%E7%9E%A7%E4%B8%80%E7%9E%A7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdmke.pixnet.net%2Fblog%2Fpost%2F220139621-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E9%2586%25AB%25E6%258A%258A%25E8%2584%2588%25E5%258E%259F%25E7%2590%2586%25EF%25BC%258C%25E6%2594%25B6%25E8%2597%258F%25E5%25A5%25BD%25EF%25BC%2581%25E6%25B2%2592%25E4%25BA%258B%25E8%2587%25AA%25E5%25B7%25B1%25E4%25B9%259F%25E8%2583%25BD%25E7%259E%25A7%25E4%25B8%2580%25E7%259E%25A7&d=RXc9xvVhXBFlPE4DV6Zf5DbTr8NPmLdj%2FTsGYWOA6so%3D&h=3153f442\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://dmke.pixnet.net/blog/post/220139621-%E4%B8%AD%E9%86%AB%E6%8A%8A%E8%84%88%E5%8E%9F%E7%90%86%EF%BC%8C%E6%94%B6%E8%97%8F%E5%A5%BD%EF%BC%81%E6%B2%92%E4%BA%8B%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E4%B9%9F%E8%83%BD%E7%9E%A7%E4%B8%80%E7%9E%A7</a>"},{"pid":"00a5db9305bec714af93282b4c9f471c9282fc12","tid":1577312,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"feb85495b6a6ce23bdf8d96084ee48490bded0c0","tid":1577312,"uid":59014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T15:36:01.000Z","msg":"把下我脈, 睇睇手掌, 伸下條利<br />\n就執左幾劑藥比你, 又話你腎虛<br />\n<br />\n我忍唔住咁快見完醫生, 事關真係病到嘔彩<br />\n問佢屋企有食呢隻野, 問佢有無用<br />\n佢搖搖頭 無直接答 最後up左某D中醫既terms <br />\n然後又搖搖頭"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T08:07:54.000Z","msg":"歷史角度思考科學醫學<br />\n<br />\n中醫同西醫唔同的地方係<br />\n中醫源自古中國<br />\n皇帝年代，君主和高官絕對有生殺權<br />\n你醫唔到佢，除時要你死<br />\n班學者先要把醫學變到神神化化野黎保命。<br />\n民國一到，開始都轉晒西醫，中醫開始就out。<br />\n<br />\n當然搞左幾千年，都有返少少料到，所以好多時都好有效，但就無咩科學根據。其實係表面無咩科學根據，內裏都有。因為古人要保命，無辦法。"}]}